Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Corporal punishment ruling
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407cdh
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 24 Apr 1977
Landmark case sees Supreme Court allow teachers to use 'reasonable' corporal punishment. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less